document_data.name: Anaharae Eroth
document_data.mainbody: '''Anaharae Eroth''' was a [[moon elf]] elder of [[House Eroth]] in [[1367 DR]].
document_data.Personality: Like her brother, [[Tanithil Eroth]], she was a skilled [[ranger]] and was rumoured to serve [[Amlaruil Moonflower|Queen Amlaruil Moonflower]].
